   De Craene, L. P. Ronse, Royal Bot Gardens Edinburgh, Edinburgh EH3 5LR, Midlothian, Scotland.
   Wanntorp, L., Swedish Museum Nat Hist, S-10405 Stockholm, Sweden.},
